'''第77届奥斯卡颁奖典礼'''是[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]旨在奖励[[2004年电影|2004年最优秀电影]]的一场晚会，于[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]2005年2月27日下午17点30分（[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]晚上20点30分）开始在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[好莱坞|好莱坞]]的[[杜比剧院|杜比剧院]]举行，共计颁发了24个类别的[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（也称[[学院奖|学院奖]]）。晚会通过[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]在[[美国电视|美国]]直播，由吉尔·凯茨担任[[制作人|制作人]]，路易斯·{{lang|en|J}}·霍维茨执导<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Feiwell | first1 = Jill | title = Familiar face in Oscar seat | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205115356/http://variety.com/2004/film/news/familiar-face-in-oscar-seat-1117911809/ | url = http://variety.com/2004/film/news/familiar-face-in-oscar-seat-1117911809/ | accessdate = 2015-02-17 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2004-10-11}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last1 = Feiwell | first1 = Jill | title = Horvitz helms Oscars again | url = http://variety.com/2004/film/news/horvitz-helms-oscars-again-1117914608/ | accessdate = 2015-02-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205114927/http://variety.com/2004/film/news/horvitz-helms-oscars-again-1117914608/ | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2004-12-04 | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，[[喜剧演员|喜剧演员]][[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]首度担任主持人<ref name="Oscar Rocks">{{cite news | last1 = LaPorte | first1 = Nicole | title = Oscar Rocks | url = http://variety.com/2004/film/news/oscar-rocks-1117911964/ | accessdate = 2015-02-17 | work = Variety | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150208054539/http://variety.com/2004/film/news/oscar-rocks-1117911964/ | publisher = PMC | date = 2004-10-14 | archivedate = 2015-02-08 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。两星期前的2月12日，女演员[[斯嘉丽·约翰逊|斯嘉丽·约翰逊]]在加利福尼亚州[[帕萨迪纳_(加利福尼亚州)|帕萨迪纳]]的[[帕萨迪纳朗廷亨廷顿酒店|丽思卡尔顿亨廷顿酒店及水疗中心]]主持颁发了[[奥斯卡科技成果奖|奥斯卡科技成果奖]]<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Slezak | first1 = Michael | title = Scarlett Fever | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205154400/http://www.ew.com/article/2005/01/24/scarlett-johansson-will-host-sci-tech-oscars | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2005/01/24/scarlett-johansson-will-host-sci-tech-oscars | accessdate = 2015-02-17 | work = Entertainment Weekly | publisher = Time Warner | date = 2005-01-24 | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

《[[神鬼玩家|神鬼玩家]]》是这个夜晚获奖最多的电影，赢得5项大奖<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Germain | first1 = David | title = Oscar 'Baby' | url = http://jacksonville.com/tu-online/stories/022805/lif_18085100.shtml | accessdate = 2015-02-17 | work = The Florida Times-Union | publisher = Morris Communications | date = 2005-02-28 | archivedate = 2015-02-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150208233116/http://jacksonville.com/tu-online/stories/022805/lif_18085100.shtml | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《[[登峰造擊|登峰造擊]]》获得包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]、[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|导演]]和[[奥斯卡最佳女主角奖|女主角]]在内的4项大奖。其他获奖作品包括胜出2项的《[[超人总动员|超人总动员]]》和《[[灵魂歌王|灵魂歌王]]》，以及获奖1项的《[[小小摄影师的异想世界|小小摄影师的异想世界]]》、《[[王牌冤家|王牌冤家]]》、《[[寻找梦幻岛|寻找梦幻岛]]》、《[[雷蒙·斯尼奇的不幸历险|雷蒙·斯尼奇的不幸历险]]》、《重大时刻：孩子们的游行》（{{lang|en|''Mighty Times: The Children's March''}}）、《[[革命前夕的摩托車日記|革命前夕的摩托車日記]]》、《[[瑞恩_(2004年短片)|瑞恩]]》（{{lang|en|''Ryan''}}）、《[[深海长眠|深海长眠]]》、《[[杯酒人生|杯酒人生]]》、《[[蜘蛛侠2|蜘蛛侠2]]》和《[[黄蜂_(2003年短片)|黄蜂]]》（{{lang|en|''Wasp''}}）。晚会的电视直播平均吸引了超过4200万美国观众收看。

== 获奖和提名 ==
2005年1月25日，[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]主席[[弗兰克·皮尔森|弗兰克·皮尔森]]与男演员[[艾德里安·布洛迪|艾德里安·布洛迪]]一起在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[比佛利山_(加利福尼亞州)|比佛利山]]的[[塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院|塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院]]公布第77届奥斯卡金像奖提名名单<ref>{{cite news | title = Oscar Watch: Brody on board for noms | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812201817/http://variety.com/2005/film/news/oscar-watch-brody-on-board-for-noms-1117916512/ | url = http://variety.com/2005/film/news/oscar-watch-brody-on-board-for-noms-1117916512/ | accessdate = 2015-02-17 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2005-01-18}}</ref>。《[[神鬼玩家|神鬼玩家]]》以11项提名领跑，《[[寻找梦幻岛|寻找梦幻岛]]》和《[[登峰造擊|登峰造擊]]》均以7项提名排在第二位<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Wloszczyna | first1 = Susan | title = 'Aviator' lands 11 Oscar nominations | accessdate = 2015-02-17 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 2005-01-25 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2005-01-25-oscar-nominations_x.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140808045650/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2005-01-25-oscar-nominations_x.htm | archivedate = 2014-08-08 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

获奖名单在2005年2月27日举行的颁奖典礼上公布<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Waxman | first1 = Sharon | title = 'Million Dollar Baby' Dominates Oscars | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2005/02/28/movies/oscars/28osca.html?_r=0 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205100712/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/02/28/movies/oscars/28osca.html?_r=0 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-02-17 | work = The New York Times | publisher = The New York Times Company | date = 2005-02-28 | archivedate = 2015-02-05}}</ref>。[[克林特·伊斯特伍德|克林特·伊斯特伍德]]以74岁高龄创下[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|导演]]奖最年长得主的新纪录<ref>{{cite book | last = Crouse | first = Richard | title = Reel Winners: Movie Award Trivia | year = 2005 | isbn = 1-55002-574-0 | location = Toronto, Canada | publisher = University of Toronto Press | page = 235}}</ref>。[[马丁·斯科塞斯|马丁·斯科塞斯]]凭《神鬼玩家》第5次获得导演奖提名，但仍然未能获奖，成为继[[罗伯特·奥特曼|罗伯特·奥特曼]]、[[克拉伦斯·布朗|克拉伦斯·布朗]]（{{lang|en|Clarence Brown}}）、[[阿尔弗雷德·希区柯克|阿尔弗雷德·希区柯克]]和[[金·维多|金·维多]]（{{lang|en|King Vidor}}）以来第5位5次提名全部落空的导演<ref name="Osborne-2008">{{cite book | last = Osborne | first = Robert | title = 80 Years of the Oscar: The Complete History of the Academy Awards | url = https://archive.org/details/80yearsofoscarof0000osbo | year = 2008 | isbn = 0-7892-0992-6 | location = New York, United States | publisher = Abbeville Publishing Group}}</ref>{{rp|366}}。[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|男主角]]奖得主[[杰米·福克斯|杰米·福克斯]]成为历史上第10位[[一年获两项奥斯卡金像奖提名演员列表|在同一年中获两项表演类奖项提名]]的演员，也是第2位达成这一目标的男演员<ref>{{cite book | last = Todd | first = Anne M. | title = Jamie Foxx | url = https://archive.org/details/jamiefoxx0000todd | year = 2008 | isbn = 978-1-60413-000-3 | location = New York, United States | publisher = Chelsea House Publishers | page = [https://archive.org/details/jamiefoxx0000todd/page/3 3]}}</ref>。[[凯特·布兰切特|凯特·布兰切特]]因在《神鬼玩家》中扮演[[凯瑟琳·赫本|凯瑟琳·赫本]]获[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|女配角]]奖，成为史上首位因出演奥斯卡金像奖得主而获奖的演员<ref name="Osborne-2008" />{{rp|368}}。《[[摩托日记_(电影)|革命前夕的摩托車日記]]》插曲《{{lang|es|Al otro lado del río}}》成为第二首赢得[[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖|原创歌曲]]奖、并且其中完全没有英语歌词的歌曲。上一次出现这种情况是在1961年的[[第33届奥斯卡金像奖|第33届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]上，[[1960年电影|1960年]]希腊电影《[[痴汉艳娃_(1960年电影)|痴汉艳娃]]》（{{lang|el|Ποτέ Την Κυριακή}}）插曲《{{lang|en|Never on Sunday}}》获得原创歌曲奖<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Gray | first1 = Tim | title = Oscar’s fistful of 'Dollar' | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205113259/http://variety.com/2005/film/news/oscar-s-fistful-of-dollar-1117918632/ | url = http://variety.com/2005/film/news/oscar-s-fistful-of-dollar-1117918632/ | accessdate = 2015-02-17 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2005-02-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

