== 典礼资讯 ==
[[File:Chris_Rock_WE_2012_Shankbone.JPG|thumb]]担任第77届奥斯卡颁奖典礼的[[主持人|主持人]]]]
为了提高晚会直播收视率，延续提名电影的关注度，制片人吉尔·凯茨决定在节目中加入年轻的新面孔，笑匠兼男演员[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]因此成为2005年颁奖典礼的主持人<ref name="Oscar Rocks" />。对此凯茨在新闻稿中表示：“我是克里斯·洛克的超级粉丝。他总是能把我逗乐，而且总是有那么些有意思的事情来说。克里斯代表着新生代最优秀的漫画（形象风格）。（能够）由他来主持奥斯卡真是太棒了。我都等不及了。”<ref>
{{cite news | title = Chris Rock to Host Oscars | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2004/10/14/chris-rock-to-host-oscars/ | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812125137/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2004/10/14/chris-rock-to-host-oscars/ | work = Fox News | publisher = 21st Century Fox | date = 2004-10-14 | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = yes }}
</ref>。这样，洛克就成为历史上首位独立主持这一盛会的[[非裔美国人|非裔美国人]]<ref>{{cite news | last1 = McNamara | first1 = Mary | title = Rock On | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2005/feb/27/magazine/tm-rock09 | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 2005-02-27 | archivedate = 2015-02-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150208063943/http://articles.latimes.com/2005/feb/27/magazine/tm-rock09}}</ref>。

洛克曾在距颁奖典礼还有近一个月时接受《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的乔什·沃尔克（{{lang|en|Josh Wolk}}）采访并表示：“拜托，这就是场时装展。没有人是在表演，这不是什么音乐节目。你看到过哪个异性恋黑人爷们儿会坐在那儿看什么奥斯卡？找一个来看看。”<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Wolk | first1 = Josh | title = The Oscars Get Rock-ed | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2005/02/01/chris-rock-talks-about-his-first-oscar-hosting-gig | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = Entertainment Weekly | publisher = Time Warner | date = 2005-02-01 | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205154426/http://www.ew.com/article/2005/02/01/chris-rock-talks-about-his-first-oscar-hosting-gig}}</ref>。这一说法引起部分反弹，政治博客写手[[马特·德拉吉|马特·德拉吉]]之后报道称，有多位美国电影艺术与科学学院会员对洛克的上述言论不满，要求取消他的主持人资格，但报道中没有提及这些成员的名字<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Grossberg | first1 = Josh | title = Rock Roiling Oscars | url = http://www.eonline.com/news/49247/rock-roiling-oscars | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = E! | publisher = NBCUniversal | date = 2005-02-15 | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205100726/http://www.eonline.com/news/49247/rock-roiling-oscars}}</ref>。为此制作人凯茨发表声明为主持人辩护：“克里斯的说法意在幽默，只是为了表明对于有些人来说——显然这有些人中还包括克里斯自己——奥斯卡颁奖典礼太闷了”<ref>{{cite news | title = Producer supports Chris Rock as show's host | url = http://old.chronicle.augusta.com/stories/2005/02/16/osc_443191.shtml | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = The Augusta Chronicle | publisher = Morris Communications | date = 2005-02-16 | archivedate = 2015年2月5日 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205090055/http://old.chronicle.augusta.com/stories/2005/02/16/osc_443191.shtml | df =  }}</ref>。此外，沃尔克还斥责了德拉吉在文章中夸大洛克言论的做法，称主持人的话并没有任何争议性<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Wolk | first1 = Josh | title = Rock and Roll | work = Entertainment Weekly | publisher = Time Warner | date = 2005-02-18 | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2005/02/18/ews-chris-rock-interviewer-weighs-matt-drudge | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205131106/http://www.ew.com/article/2005/02/18/ews-chris-rock-interviewer-weighs-matt-drudge | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。 [[男、女同性恋者反诽谤联盟|男、女同性恋者反诽谤联盟]]执行主席琼·加里（{{lang|en|Joan Garry}}）也针对这一争议言论发表声明：“克里斯·洛克不是在取笑同性恋——他是在调侃奥斯卡”<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Britt | first1 = Donna | title = Drudge Takes the Oscar for 'Clueless' | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A33625-2005Feb17.html | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = The Washington Post | publisher = The Washington Post Company | date = 2005-02-18 | archive-date = 2015-02-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205092152/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A33625-2005Feb17.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。洛克在颁奖典礼前的最后一个星期一登上《[[杰·雷诺今夜秀|杰·雷诺今夜秀]]》（{{lang|en|''The Tonight Show with Jay Leno''}}）澄清自己的言论。主持人[[杰·雷诺|雷诺]]问起时，洛克回答：“我可没说那样的话，我说的是只有同性恋才看[[托尼奖|托尼奖颁奖典礼]]。”不过他又重申：“我还真没见过哪位不在演艺圈混、并且也不是同性恋的爷们儿会去看奥斯卡颁奖典礼。”<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Moloshok | first1 = Danny | title = Chris Rock clarifies Oscar comments | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205123022/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2005-02-22-rock-oscar-comments_x.htm | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | deadurl = no | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2005-02-22-rock-oscar-comments_x.htm | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 2005-02-22}}</ref>

颁奖典礼的流程做了多项调整，以期让节目进行更流畅、互动性更强，并缩短晚会的持续时间。盖茨宣布，获部分奖项提名的电影人会在颁奖嘉宾宣读提名前就到达舞台<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Schodolski | first1 = Vincent J. | title = Hipper, shorter, edgier Oscars: Ceremony undergoes nips/tucks | url = http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2005-02-17/features/0502170055_1_nominees-77th-academy-awards-gil-cates | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = Chicago Tribune | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 2005-02-17 | archive-date = 2014-08-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140808052808/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2005-02-17/features/0502170055_1_nominees-77th-academy-awards-gil-cates | dead-url = no }}</ref>。还有些奖项的颁奖会直接在台下的观众席中进行<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Keller | first1 = Julie | title = Oscars Timely Makeover | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150207100051/http://www.eonline.com/news/49191/oscar-s-timely-makeovers | deadurl = no | url = http://www.eonline.com/news/49191/oscar-s-timely-makeovers | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = E! | publisher = NBCUniversal | date = 2005-02-08 | archivedate = 2015-02-07}}</ref>。此外，艺术指导设计师罗伊·克里斯托弗（{{lang|en|Roy Christopher}}）为颁奖典礼设计了一个融致敬过去和展望未来于一身的舞台，这个舞台包含有26台悬挂在前12排观众上方的[[高清视频|高清视频]]显示器，舞台地板下方还有长达12.19米{{lang|en|[[发光二极管|LED]]}}显示屏<ref>{{cite news | title = Oscar set will blur line between performers, audience | url = http://old.chronicle.augusta.com/stories/021905/osc_set.shtml | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = The Augusta Chronicle | publisher = Morris Communications | date = 2005-02-17 | archivedate = 2015年2月7日 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150207095846/http://old.chronicle.augusta.com/stories/021905/osc_set.shtml | df =  }}</ref>。颁奖嘉宾上台颁奖时，这些显示屏上会显示之前奥斯卡颁奖典礼的部分镜头；电视转播插播广告时，这些显示屏又会随机播放一些电影片段<ref>{{cite news | title = Oscars take on an interactive feel | archivedate = 2015-02-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150207120239/http://www.today.com/id/6989524/ns/today-today_entertainment/t/oscars-take-interactive-feel/#.U9qz_GOHRcp | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = NBC News | publisher = NBCUniversal | date = 2005-02-17 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.today.com/id/6989524/ns/today-today_entertainment/t/oscars-take-interactive-feel/#.U9qz_GOHRcp}}</ref>。舞台中央还有23座真人大小的奥斯卡小金人像，以不同姿态围绕舞台盘旋<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Bowles | first1 = Scott | title = Look up and look out: Academy Awards get ready to rock | archivedate = 2015-02-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150207100117/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2005-02-17-oscar-stage_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2005-02-17-oscar-stage_x.htm | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 2005-02-17}}</ref>。

另外还有多人参与了颁奖典礼的制作。电影配乐师兼音乐家比尔·康堤（{{lang|en|Bill Conti}}）担任晚会音乐总监和管弦乐队指挥<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Thompson | first1 = Jenn | title = Oscarcast vets return | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812201903/http://variety.com/2004/film/news/oscarcast-vets-return-1117915000/ | url = http://variety.com/2004/film/news/oscarcast-vets-return-1117915000/ | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2004-12-14 | archivedate = 2014-08-12}}</ref>。艺术与科学学院图形设计师布雷特·戴维森（{{lang|en|Brett Davidson}}）为晚会设计了官方海报，其主体是奥斯卡小金人上半身的正面像，背后则有4种不同的颜色方块<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Feiwell | first1 = Jill | title = Acad drawn to staffer’s design | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812201922/http://variety.com/2004/film/news/acad-drawn-to-staffer-s-design-1117913624/ | url = http://variety.com/2004/film/news/acad-drawn-to-staffer-s-design-1117913624/ | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2004-12-16}}</ref>。自由制片人科奇斯（{{lang|en|Cochise}}）和传媒公司“挖掘和媒体岛”制作的预告片在全美各地电影院放映，其中包括过去奥斯卡颁奖典礼的片段，背景则是上文提及海报中的四种颜色方块。预告片中还包含有[[黑眼豆豆|黑眼豆豆]]表演的歌曲《{{lang|en|Hey Mama}}》。<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Chang | first1 = Justin | title = Oscars hitched to trailer | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812201942/https://variety.com/2005/film/news/oscars-hitched-to-trailer-1117916390/ | url = https://variety.com/2005/film/news/oscars-hitched-to-trailer-1117916390/ | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2005-01-16 | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。晚会开幕时展现电影发展史的片段旁白由两次获奥斯卡最佳男主角奖的[[达斯汀·霍夫曼|达斯汀·霍夫曼]]解说<ref name="WaPo Oscars" />。

=== 提名电影票房表现 ===
截至1月25日提名公布时，全部5部获最佳影片奖提名的电影在美国[[票房|票房]]市场表现都没有达到大片标准，没有任何一部登上2004年度电影票房十强榜单，是继1986年以来首次出现这种情况<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Gray | first1 = Brandon | title = 'Aviator,' 'Million Dollar Baby' Get Best Picture Boost | archivedate = 2014-12-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141215002732/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=1670&p=.htm | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=1670&p=.htm | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = Box Office Mojo | publisher = Amazon.com | date = 2014-01-31}}</ref>。同时，全部5部最佳影片奖提名作品在颁奖典礼前所售出的电影票总数量也创下1984年以来的新低<ref>{{cite news | title = Ticket sales are slow for best-picture nominees | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150207083310/http://old.chronicle.augusta.com/stories/2005/02/17/osc_443399.shtml | url = http://old.chronicle.augusta.com/stories/2005/02/17/osc_443399.shtml | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = The August Chronicle | publisher = Morris Communications | date = 2005-02-17 | archivedate = 2015年2月7日 | df =  }}</ref>。这其中《灵魂歌王》以7307万5825美元位居榜首，之后分别是收入5846万5000美元的《神鬼玩家》、进账3271万2690美元的《寻找梦幻岛》、收入3242万8941美元的《杯酒人生》和进账849万9006美元的《登峰造擊》<ref name="BestPictureBoxOffice">{{cite news | title = 2004 Academy Award Nominations and Winner for Best Picture | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=2004&p=.htm | work = Box Office Mojo | publisher = Amazon.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150207093404/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=2004&p=.htm | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | archivedate = 2015-02-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。提名公布时，平均每部最佳影片提名电影的票房收入为4103万6292美元<ref name="BestPictureBoxOffice" />。

在2004年[[美国电影|美国电影]]票房50强中，有14部电影获得了共计44项提名。其中《怪物史瑞克2》（[[冠军|冠军]]）、《超人总动员》（第4名）、《鲨鱼黑帮》（第11名）、《借刀杀人》（第22名）、《灵魂歌王》（第37名）和《神鬼玩家》（第49名）获得最佳影片、导演、动画长片或是任意一项演员、编剧类奖项提名<ref name="boxofficemojooscars">{{cite news | title = 2004 Yearly Box Office Results (January 24, 2005) | publisher = Amazon.com | work = Box Office Mojo | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006102117/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=2005-01-24&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=2004&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=2005-01-24&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=2004&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm}}</ref>。另外8部获提名的电影分别是《蜘蛛侠2》（[[亚军|亚军]]）、《耶稣受难记》（[[季军|季军]]）、《哈利·波特与阿兹卡班的囚徒》（第5名）、《极地特快》（第10名）、《我，机器人》（第12名）、《特洛伊》（第13名）、《雷蒙·斯尼奇的不幸历险》（第18名）和《神秘村》（第20名）<ref name="boxofficemojooscars" />。

=== 裘德·洛风波 ===
主持人克里斯·洛克在晚会开场后的独白表演桥段开玩笑道：“[[克林特·伊斯特伍德|克林特·伊斯特伍德]]是个明星，好吧？[[托比·马奎尔|托比·马奎尔]]就不过是个穿着紧身衣的男孩子了。”然后他又说道：“你想要的是[[汤姆·克鲁斯|汤姆·克鲁斯]]，但事到临头却只摊上[[裘德·洛|裘德·洛]]？不是吧。你想要[[罗素·克劳|罗素·克劳]]但却只得到[[柯林·法瑞尔|柯林·法瑞尔]]？不是吧。《[[亚历山大大帝_(电影)|亚历山大大帝]]》可不是《[[角斗士_(电影)|角斗士]]》。”面对这样的调侃，西恩·潘反驳洛克的言论，称赞裘德·洛是他这一代人中“最好的演员”之一。<ref>{{cite news | title = Host Chris Rock comes out swinging | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150212170804/http://www.today.com/id/7042377/ns/today-today_entertainment/t/host-chris-rock-comes-out-swinging/#.U9wAcmOHRco | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = NBC News | publisher = NBC Universal | date = 2005-02-28 | archivedate = 2015-02-12 | url = http://www.today.com/id/7042377/ns/today-today_entertainment/t/host-chris-rock-comes-out-swinging/#.U9wAcmOHRco}}</ref>此事过去一年多后，洛在接受《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》专栏作家克雷格·莫德诺（{{lang|en|Craig Modderno}}）采访时表示对洛克当时的话感到愤怒：“起初我一笑置之，还以为他不认识我。接下来他的话变得针对个人，这让我很生气。我的朋友们都气坏了。很遗憾我那时同时有5部还是6部电影要上映。”<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Modderno | first1 = Craig | title = Jude Law Is an Actor in Demand | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2006/09/03/movies/03modd.html?ref=movies | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = The New York Times | publisher = The New York Times Company | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150212170619/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/09/03/movies/03modd.html?ref=movies | date = 2006-09-03 | archivedate = 2015-02-12}}</ref>

=== 罗宾·威廉姆斯献唱环节取消 ===
[[罗宾·威廉姆斯|罗宾·威廉姆斯]]原计划在颁发动画长片奖时演唱[[马克·施艾曼|马克·施艾曼]]（{{lang|en|Marc Shaiman}}）和[[斯科特·惠特曼|斯科特·惠特曼]]（{{lang|en|Scott Wittman}}）创作的幽默歌曲，讽刺有关[[爱家基金会|爱家基金会]]的争议和[[我们是一家基金会|我们是一家基金会]]赞助的音乐视频，视频中有包括[[海绵宝宝|海绵宝宝]]在内的动画角色演唱歌曲《{{lang|en|We Are Family}}》（意为《我们是一家》）。威廉姆斯原定演唱的歌曲中有大意如下的歌词：“[[木偶奇遇记_(电影)|匹诺曹]]整了鼻子！[[睡美人_(电影)|睡美人]]在嗑药！[[三只小猪|三只小猪]]不符合[[犹太人|犹太人]]的戒律！[[贝蒂娃娃|贝蒂娃娃]]在比佛利山上班！”<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Shaiman | first1 = Marc | title = Robin Williams' Oscar Gag | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2005/03/07/oscar-song-network-didnt-want-you-hear | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = Entertainment Weekly | publisher = Time Warner | date = 2005-03-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150218163820/http://www.ew.com/article/2005/03/07/oscar-song-network-didnt-want-you-hear | archivedate = 2015-02-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>但凯茨和美国广播公司高管认为歌曲内容过于低俗和冒犯，此后施艾曼和惠特曼试图改写歌词，但无法达到理想的效果，因此整首歌曲都被取消<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Halbfinger | first1 = David M. | title = Cut From the Oscars: Cartoon Characters' Sins | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2005/02/27/movies/oscars/27williams.html?8br&_r=0 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140811012558/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/02/27/movies/oscars/27williams.html?8br&_r=0 | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = The New York Times | publisher = The New York Times Company | date = 2005-02-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。威廉姆斯最终仍按之前的安排颁发动画长片奖，但他还是通过自己的方式表示抗议，走上台时，他步伐缓慢，并且嘴上缠有胶带，直到说话时才取下来<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Wloszczyna | first1 = Susan | title = Williams will be heard but not seen | archivedate = 2014-08-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140808123030/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2005-03-06-robin-williams-main_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2005-03-06-robin-williams-main_x.htm | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 2005-03-07}}</ref>。

=== 专业评价 ===
媒体出版物对本届颁奖晚会评价褒贬不一，部分媒体反响较为负面。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》电视评论员罗伯特·比安科（{{lang|en|Robert Bianco}}）严厉批评洛克的表现：“喧哗、挖苦，令人不屑一顾，他（的表现）不但让人失望，简直就是历史上最糟糕的主持人。”他还认为，同时颁发多个技术类奖项的做法令人尴尬，对提名电影人缺乏足够尊重。<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Bianco | first1 = Robert | title = Alas, format did not do Oscar proud | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205052815/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2005-02-28-bianco-review_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2005-02-28-bianco-review_x.htm | accessdate = 2015-02-19 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 2005-02-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>《[[圣地牙哥联合论坛报|圣地牙哥联合论坛报]]》（{{lang|en|''U-T San Diego''}}）专栏作家罗伯特·劳伦斯（{{lang|en|Robert. P. Lawrence}}）评价：“表现中规中矩到令人扼腕，这种无法模仿的好莱坞式相互吹捧整整持续了3小时12分钟。”之后他还表示，虽然洛克的开场前卫且挑衅意味十足，但随着夜色渐深，主持人的幽默和精力都在不断走下坡路。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lawrence |first1=Robert P. |title=Even Chris Rock came off as tepid and tame at the Oscars |archivedate=2015-02-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205004937/http://www.utsandiego.com/uniontrib/20050228/news_1c28laurencm.html |url=http://www.utsandiego.com/uniontrib/20050228/news_1c28laurencm.html |accessdate=2015-02-18 |work=U-T San Diego |publisher=MLIM Holdings |date=2005-02-28 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>文斯·堀内（{{lang|en|Vince Horiuchi}}）在《[[盐湖城论坛报|盐湖城论坛报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Salt Lake Tribune''}}）上批评洛克的表现：“他完全沉浸陷在老掉牙的笑话中不能自拔（没有任何一位获奖者‘类固醇检测呈阳性’），开场独白生硬乏味（甚至都没提到自己之前有关奥斯卡颁奖典礼的那些引起争议的话），喜剧表演令人厌烦（看上去就像[[凯瑟琳·泽塔-琼斯|凯瑟琳·泽塔-琼斯]]加上[[亚当·桑德勒|亚当·桑德勒]]）。”文章中还进一步批评晚会的演员表现“死气沉沉”，制作“笨手笨脚”。<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Horiuchi | first1 = Vincent | title = If they give Oscars for boring, this year's broadcast wins big | work = The Salt Lake Tribune | publisher = MediaNew Group | date = 2005-02-28 | page = C7}}</ref>

其它媒体出版物的看法更为正面。影评人[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]认为，“说话速度很快的”洛克给节目带来“精力十足”的开局，他还称赞“克里斯·洛克用开场独白打出了本垒打，这场独角戏一针见血、主旨分明，而且毫不避讳争议，让人喜出望外”<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Ebert | first1 = Roger | title = 'Baby' Stages Late-Round Oscar Rally | deadurl = no | url = http://www.rogerebert.com/festivals-and-awards/baby-stages-late-round-oscar-rally | accessdate = 2015-02-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150207054926/http://www.rogerebert.com/festivals-and-awards/baby-stages-late-round-oscar-rally | work = Chicago Sun-Times | publisher = Sun-Times Media Group | date = 2005-02-27 | archivedate = 2015-02-07}}</ref>。电视评论员弗雷泽·摩尔（{{lang|en|Frazier Moore}}）评价洛克的表现让人“精神为之一振，（他的）主持手法细腻而不失俏皮。”他对晚会的印象甚佳：“总体而言节目表现轻松，但又不致太过匆忙。感觉就像在强调自身重要性的老调长谈中呈现出现代、清新和自由。”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Moore |first1=Frazier |title=Breezy pace scores a win for the Oscars |url=http://alb.merlinone.net/mweb/wmsql.wm.request?oneimage&imageid=6325353 |accessdate=2015-02-19 |work=Times Union |publisher=Hearst Corporation |date=2005-02-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140806062043/http://alb.merlinone.net/mweb/wmsql.wm.request?oneimage&imageid=6325353 |archivedate=2014-08-06 }}</ref>。《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》杂志的布莱恩·洛瑞（{{lang|en|Brian Lowry}}）对洛克的评价为中等，但对整场晚会表现还是感到满意<ref name="Variety Oscars" />。

=== 收视率 ===
本届颁奖典礼通过美国广播公司在美国直播，其播出时段里平均有4214万观众收看，与[[第76届奥斯卡金像奖|前一年]]相比降低了3%<ref name="Ratings">{{cite news | title = Fox, ‘Idol’ find sweeps groove | last = Kiseell | first = Rick | date = 2005-03-02 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | accessdate = 2015-02-18 | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205115036/http://variety.com/2005/scene/news/fox-idol-find-sweeps-groove-1117918745/ | url = http://variety.com/2005/scene/news/fox-idol-find-sweeps-groove-1117918745/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。从尼尔森收视率调查的数据看，节目的表现也不及去年，吸收了25.4%的家庭观众，收视率超过38%<ref name="Ratings" /><ref name="Adage">{{cite news | last1 = Atkinson | first1 = Claire | title = Final Oscar Ratings Contradict Early Reports | url = http://adage.com/article/media/final-oscar-tv-ratings-contradict-early-reports/45224/ | accessdate = 2015-02-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150205112245/http://adage.com/article/media/final-oscar-tv-ratings-contradict-early-reports/45224/ | archivedate = 2015-02-05 | work = Advertising Age | publisher = Crain Communications | date = 2005-03-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。此外，节目在18至49岁年龄段收获的收视率为15.1/34，这意味着当时美国所有该年龄段人群中有15.1%观看了本届奥斯卡颁奖典礼，而当时有看电视的该年龄段观众群则有34%收看本节目<ref name="Ratings" />。

